	* src/gtk/x11opt.c (DefaultDialogClose): add preserve_width.
	(MiscDialogSetupItem): add preserve_width.
	(MiscDialogSetup): add preserve_width.
	(MiscDialogClose): add preserve_width.
	(MiscDialogClose): add preserve_width.

